        <updateDate>2006-10-10T14:14:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Landfill Gas Act of 2006 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a business-related tax credit for the production of natural gas at a high Btu fuel facility (a facility that produces high Btu biomass fuel and is placed in service before January 1, 2012). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
